# Simple Business Card

This project is a simple business card created entirely with HTML and CSS. It serves as a basic example of how to structure and style a business card using only these two technologies.

## Features

- **Pure HTML and CSS**: The business card is built using only HTML for the structure and CSS for the styling, making it easy to understand and modify.
- **Basic Layout**: The design is kept simple to focus on the essentials of a business card layout.
